title: Genome resequencing of Vanilla planifolia
design_description: Genomic DNA was extracted from all lyophilized leaf samples using the Qiagen DNeasy Plant Mini Kit following the manufacturer's protocol. Genomic DNA samples were sent to Genewiz (now Azenta) for library preparation and sequencing of 150bp paired-end reads using an Illumina HiSeq platform.
